== Trivia ==
She made an appearance as a map-specific drop for Episode 3 in the special rescue event from December 15 to 22, 2016, and again from May 13 to 19, 2017.

She is also the map-specific drop for level 1-3 and 3-3 in the collaboration event between Girls' Frontline and ''DJMAX RESPECT''.

